itunes:title: Doing a Reset for a Better Life - Part 2
title: Doing a Reset for a Better Life - Part 2
description: God is a God of newness. He doesn't do the same old things all the time. To live a better life, you need to cooperate with the new things God wants to do in your family, in your career, in your friendships, in his church, and in the world around you.
